    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/ywhwyf-mp/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=626145920047645235&sectionId=626145920114754099)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7RNJikUOC_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg7RNJikUOC_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.trustpilot.net/brand-assets/4.1.0/stars/stars-5.svg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpcOr3wu4V_text","label":"ggpcOr3wu4V_text","default":"<p>4.8 Rating from 40,000+ Women Over 40</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggnmVBp968_background_desktop_image_src","label":"gggnmVBp968_background_desktop_image_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/26_be782b21-f813-44c1-ab11-a6cb8ba90b82.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gggnmVBp968_background_mobile_image_src","label":"gggnmVBp968_background_mobile_image_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/27_ace1b6c6-7eb7-4c4d-aa57-1e98b866806d.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggq2lIdaxVj_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggq2lIdaxVj_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/time.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYBpNCKQEe_text","label":"ggYBpNCKQEe_text","default":"<p>5 min read</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeD30gVc-o_text","label":"ggeD30gVc-o_text","default":"<p>Wellness&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZ27ga1epy_text","label":"ggZ27ga1epy_text","default":"<p>Health</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkW-tYQbCN_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggkW-tYQbCN_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/time.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbVhH8yvsM_text","label":"ggbVhH8yvsM_text","default":"<p>5 min read</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj2MlbgPci_text","label":"ggj2MlbgPci_text","default":"Top UK Skincare Expert:&nbsp;Most Anti-Aging Creams Are Designed to Fail — Here’s Why"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsdxtqBRbP_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggsdxtqBRbP_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/WhatsApp_Image_2025-07-26_at_12.07.50_AM.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMTtLiPXuX_text","label":"ggMTtLiPXuX_text","default":"<p>Dr. Nicole - Dermatologist Skincare Expert | July 25, 2025</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdBueX8lW6_text","label":"ggdBueX8lW6_text","default":"No one tells you how hard it gets to feel good in your own skin."},{"type":"html","id":"ggFaqI6AhAS_text","label":"ggFaqI6AhAS_text","default":"<p>After 20 years of treating women in their 40s, 50s, and beyond, I started to notice something strange. The same skincare routines that once worked… <strong>just didn’t anymore</strong>. That’s when I started recommending something different—something that melts into the skin, locks in moisture, and delivers active ingredients exactly where they’re needed.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpjjghbq4w_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggpjjghbq4w_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/1_3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQJM9d_fA5_text","label":"ggQJM9d_fA5_text","default":"<p><strong>Dry, sagging skin. Loss of glow. Fine lines that show up overnight…</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>These aren’t just signs of aging—they’re signs that your skin barrier is asking for deeper support.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Let me explain what most skincare routines miss (and how to fix it)…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZHuYgoc8x_text","label":"ggZHuYgoc8x_text","default":"Turns Out, It Was Never About Moisturizer"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1R8B5603q_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg1R8B5603q_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/2_2_bc6e9869-8b0c-40a7-802f-b07c4e343968.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvDN5djePx_text","label":"ggvDN5djePx_text","default":"<p>Once you hit 40, something shifts. You&nbsp;<strong>notice fine lines</strong> forming overnight.&nbsp;<strong>Skin feels drier</strong>. That natural glow? It’s not showing up like it used to.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You try serums, oils, and expensive creams. You might even try micro-needling or supplements. But despite your efforts, something still feels off.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>What if the solution isn’t more products?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>What if it’s deeper absorption?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBbddocv6g_text","label":"ggBbddocv6g_text","default":"If Your Skincare Routine Feels Useless Lately—This Might Be Why"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrD8PpVsoT_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggrD8PpVsoT_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/3_2_f885b774-c84c-40f5-b34d-f79efe566516.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3DTBKTk91_text","label":"gg3DTBKTk91_text","default":"<p>By the time you reach your 40s, your skin begins to feel different—less firm, more fragile.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>There’s a biological reason for that shift.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Collagen production drops by up to 30% by age 45.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>By 50, most women have lost more than&nbsp;<strong>50% of their total collagen.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>What’s behind it?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0cbJmzijF_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg0cbJmzijF_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/4_2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdDSyRsumR_text","label":"ggdDSyRsumR_text","default":"<p><strong>Estrogen levels fall by as much as 60% during menopause.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Estrogen plays a key role in regulating collagen. As it declines, so does your skin’s ability to stay plump and elastic.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Fibroblasts—the cells that produce collagen—slow down by 50%.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>These cells become less active and efficient with age, producing lower-quality collagen and fewer new fibers.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1iNsNi9_B_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg1iNsNi9_B_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/5_2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggomlV8M0o4_text","label":"ggomlV8M0o4_text","default":"<p><strong>Skin thickness drops by about 1% every year after menopause.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Over a decade, this adds up—contributing to thinning, sagging, and visible signs of aging.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Antioxidant levels drop by up to 30%.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>With less natural protection, your skin becomes more vulnerable to UV and environmental stress, which accelerates collagen breakdown.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvwGd8HYnL_text","label":"ggvwGd8HYnL_text","default":"Here’s what’s happening beneath the surface:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCGUOU9Opq_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggCGUOU9Opq_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/6_2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_YI0623V__text","label":"gg_YI0623V__text","default":"<ul><li>Your skin loses hydration faster<br>The lipid layer that locks in moisture gets thinner. Even rich creams evaporate quickly.<br>&nbsp;</li><li>Barrier repair slows<br>Your skin becomes more reactive, with more redness, flaking, and dullness.<br>&nbsp;</li><li>Collagen and elastin production plummet<br>This causes sagging, fine lines, and that loss of plumpness you can&nbsp;feel.<br>&nbsp;</li><li>Most skincare doesn’t even absorb properly<br>Short-term products evaporate or sit on top without penetrating where they’re needed.</li></ul>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxaVG4LW-m_text","label":"ggxaVG4LW-m_text","default":"I Started Looking at Skincare Differently.&nbsp;<u>That’s When Everything Changed.</u>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggspN2seyfv_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggspN2seyfv_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/WhatsApp_Image_2025-07-26_at_12.07.50_AM.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOz-DlfJR4_text","label":"ggOz-DlfJR4_text","default":"<p>After working with hundreds of women over 40, I realized:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It’s not that your skincare is “bad.” It’s that your skin has changed—and no one’s told you how to care for it now.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Most products are built for surface-level fixes.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But aging skin needs&nbsp;deeper absorption… slower release… and ingredients that actually reach beneath the surface.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>That’s when I found a smarter solution.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>One that works&nbsp;with your skin’s new needs—not against them.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJ2lK3M065_text","label":"ggJ2lK3M065_text","default":"40,000+ Women Tried It. Here’s What They Said:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCs_GslXrj_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggCs_GslXrj_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/8_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggofcUJzsPe_text","label":"ggofcUJzsPe_text","default":"<p>In a large-scale customer survey of&nbsp;<strong>40,000+ women between the ages of 35 and 65</strong>, participants shared what happened after using Nifora’s mask:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSXYQf-SgK_text","label":"ggSXYQf-SgK_text","default":"88% saw visibly plumper skin within 3 hours"},{"type":"html","id":"ggO9-WywQzX_text","label":"ggO9-WywQzX_text","default":"Fine lines looked softer, and skin felt fuller—especially around the eyes, cheeks, and jaw."},{"type":"html","id":"ggSHyFXiXEe_text","label":"ggSHyFXiXEe_text","default":"91% felt calm, deeply hydrated skin for over 24 hours"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1i_Uxw4Uw_text","label":"gg1i_Uxw4Uw_text","default":"Users with dry or menopausal skin said it soothed irritation and locked in moisture."},{"type":"html","id":"ggALTP79Q6e_text","label":"ggALTP79Q6e_text","default":"84% noticed smoother, more even tone after 2 weeks"},{"type":"html","id":"ggs0YA1fIA1_text","label":"ggs0YA1fIA1_text","default":"Less redness, fewer blotches, and a glow that didn’t need makeup."},{"type":"html","id":"ggmo-8o2UZv_text","label":"ggmo-8o2UZv_text","default":"78% reordered within 30 days"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWUXXaJBKI_text","label":"ggWUXXaJBKI_text","default":"Most didn’t want to go a week without it—many replaced their old masks entirely."},{"type":"html","id":"gg9mCVvepAi_text","label":"gg9mCVvepAi_text","default":"So What’s the Real Fix for Aging Skin?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdFCjg57wh_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggdFCjg57wh_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/9_0f03ff7d-8c30-4b14-b5b1-fcb3ccb1a7e8.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggF5ZX1vn4f_text","label":"ggF5ZX1vn4f_text","default":"<p>This isn’t your typical one-and-done sheet mask.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It’s not a 10-minute glow-up before an event.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It’s a longer, intentional treatment that fits your life—not rushes it.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Nifora’s mask melts into the skin, hugging every contour like a second skin.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It slowly delivers active ingredients—like hydrolyzed marine collagen, niacinamide, and hyaluronic acid—deep into the skin, where they’re needed most.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6ehnir0yF_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg6ehnir0yF_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/10_ff63b95f-c6ff-4a9d-8aaa-b6481a39509d.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggY0hxUc0s9_text","label":"ggY0hxUc0s9_text","default":"<p>This is skincare that works while you rest.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It respects your time, your skin, and your stage of life.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>For many women, it has become a weekly ritual.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>One that actually delivers visible results—plumper skin, firmer texture, and a glow that lasts.</p>"}],
